Ctrl + A

Ctrl + Shift + Space

Undo

Ctrl + Z

Redo

Ctrl + Y

Ctrl + Shift + Z

Find

Ctrl + F

Find and replace

Ctrl + H

Save

Every change is saved automatically in Drive

Ctrl + S

Open

Ctrl + O

Print

Ctrl + P

Copy

Ctrl + C

Cut

Ctrl + X

Paste

Ctrl + V

Paste values only

Ctrl + Shift + V

Show common keyboard shortcuts

Ctrl + /

